---
title: Eggplant & Sun-Dried Tomato Pasta
description: Sun-dried tomatoes are the secret to sweet, rich tomato flavor without hours of stovetop simmering. Adding roasted eggplant into the sauce deepens the richness even further. Maker sure to season the sauce the sauce at every step of the way for intense layers of flavor!
